# Normalize line endings across all platforms.
#
# Without this, contributors on Windows (with core.autocrlf=true) have their
# checkouts converted to CRLF. Running `cargo test` then rewrites the committed
# test snapshot JSONs under contracts/*/test_snapshots/ with CRLF endings,
# making ~30 byte-identical files show up as modified on every local run.
#
# Forcing LF keeps the working tree consistent with the repo's existing all-LF
# convention regardless of each contributor's local git config.

# Auto-detect text files and always check them out with LF endings.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Be explicit about the test snapshot format so the intent is obvious even if
# the broad default above is ever narrowed.
*.json text eol=lf
